### 4.4 API Endpoints

#### Checklist Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth | Roles |
|--------|----------|-------------|------|-------|
| GET | `/checklists` | List all checklists (paginated) | JWT | All authenticated |
| POST | `/checklists` | Create new checklist | JWT | manager_roles |
| GET | `/checklists/:id` | Get checklist with items | JWT | All authenticated |
| PUT | `/checklists/:id` | Update checklist | JWT | manager_roles |
| DELETE | `/checklists/:id` | Soft delete checklist | JWT | manager_roles |
| POST | `/checklists/:id/restore` | Restore deleted checklist | JWT | manager_roles |

#### Checklist Item Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth | Roles |
|--------|----------|-------------|------|-------|
| POST | `/checklists/:id/items` | Add item to checklist | JWT | manager_roles |
| PUT | `/checklists/:id/items/:item_id` | Update item | JWT | manager_roles |
| DELETE | `/checklists/:id/items/:item_id` | Remove item | JWT | manager_roles |
| PATCH | `/checklists/:id/items/:item_id/toggle` | Toggle completion | JWT | all_wo_roles |
| POST | `/checklists/:id/complete-all` | Mark all items complete | JWT | all_wo_roles |

### 4.5 Request/Response Formats

#### Create Checklist

**Request:**
```json
{
  "name": "Preventive Maintenance Checklist",
  "description": "Standard PM tasks for HVAC units",
  "work_order_id": "uuid-string (optional)",
  "asset_id": "uuid-string (optional)",
  "pm_schedule_id": "uuid-string (optional)",
  "is_required": false,
  "items": [
    { "description": "Inspect air filters", "order_index": 0 },
    { "description": "Check refrigerant levels", "order_index": 1 },
    { "description": "Clean condenser coils", "order_index": 2 }
  ]
}
```

**Response (201):**
```json
{
  "id": "uuid-string",
  "org_id": "uuid-string",
  "name": "Preventive Maintenance Checklist",
  "description": "Standard PM tasks for HVAC units",
  "is_required": false,
  "is_active": true,
  "created_by": "uuid-string",
  "created_at": "2026-03-27T10:00:00Z",
  "items": [
    { "id": "uuid", "description": "Inspect air filters", "order_index": 0, "is_completed": false },
    { "id": "uuid", "description": "Check refrigerant levels", "order_index": 1, "is_completed": false },
    { "id": "uuid", "description": "Clean condenser coils", "order_index": 2, "is_completed": false }
  ]
}
```

#### Toggle Item Completion

**Request:**
```json
PATCH /checklists/{checklist_id}/items/{item_id}/toggle
```

**Response (200):**
```json
{
  "id": "uuid-string",
  "description": "Inspect air filters",
  "order_index": 0,
  "is_completed": true,
  "completed_by": "uuid-string",
  "completed_at": "2026-03-27T10:15:00Z"
}
```

