### 6.2 Required Checklist Validation (Optional)

When Work Order status changes to `completed` or `pending_review`:

```typescript
// In work order status update logic
const checklist = await checklistService.getByWorkOrderId(workOrderId);
if (checklist?.is_required && !allItemsComplete(checklist)) {
  throw new BadRequestError('Please complete all required checklist items');
}
```

