## 9. UI/UX Design

### 9.1 Color Scheme

Follow existing CMMS platform design tokens:

| Element | Light Mode | Dark Mode |
|---------|-----------|-----------|
| Primary | `#1a365d` | `#63b3ed` |
| Success (completed) | `#38a169` | `#68d391` |
| Pending | `#d69e2e` | `#faf089` |
| Required badge | `#e53e3e` | `#fc8181` |

### 9.2 Component States

**Checklist Item States:**
- **Pending:** Default checkbox, normal text
- **Completed:** Checked checkbox, strikethrough text (optional), muted color
- **Disabled:** Grayed out, no interaction

**Progress Indicator:**
- Visual progress bar with percentage
- Color changes: < 50% yellow, 50-99% blue, 100% green

### 9.3 Responsive Design

- Mobile: Stack items vertically, full-width buttons
- Tablet: 2-column layout for forms
- Desktop: Full layout with sidebar

