## 12. Risk Assessment

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Scope creep | Medium | High | Clear scope definition; defer optional features |
| Integration complexity | Low | Medium | Start with standalone checklist first |
| Performance with large lists | Low | Low | Add pagination for items if needed |
| Concurrent edit conflicts | Low | Low | Implement optimistic locking if needed |

